originalText.text:
I am writing a review of this Dr. on behalf of my sister, because she was too angry to say anything to Dr. Kazim and just wanted to get out of his office. He is the most arrogant, obnoxious, imperious Dr. she has ever been to and she has been to many. He may be a good clinician in his field as an oculoplastic surgeon but he has the bedside manner of Dr. Mengele. He carries the Dr. omnipotence just a "tad" too far. How dare he speak to my sister that way. I would have never left his office without telling him where he can put his attitude. SHAME ON HIM.

One star review is one star too many for this individual.
